      • starter

        public static void starter(SetUp setup)
        This method starter will set up the in-game page of pacman starter(SetUp) This method takes an instance of SetUp as input and generate corresponding game board based on settings sample.SetUp The method will first create a game manager with a base javafx group. Then the game manager will be initialized by settings. Finally game manager will create the in-game scene with the base javafx group sample.GameManager.drawBoard
        @param setup the setting package contains all customization information
